es-challenge-bolivia-the-drug-hub" ><img src="/images/Investigations/bolivia_drug_hub/bolivia1.jpg" alt="Evo's Challenge: Bolivia the Drug Hub" /><span class="image-title">Evo's Challenge: Bolivia the Drug Hub</span> </a></li></ul></li></ul>

